org.openbel.framework.common.model
Class CommonModelFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.common.model.CommonModelFactory

public final class CommonModelFactory
extends Object

CommonModelFactory represents a factory for common model BEL objects. The factory deals with managing the construction of common model objects in order to reduce redundant object creation.

For instance, any String used in a common model will be managed in the a local Map in order to reduce duplicate String objects.

The CommonModelFactory is a singleton class. To obtain the single reference access the static getInstance().

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>
